{"tid":2355594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"共產黨最叻就係散播恐懼","createTime":"2021-01-06T08:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T09:16:57.000Z","uid":146351,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"621116889ec610e6e0532164813f8833956eb5c9","tid":2355594,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"共產黨最叻就係散播恐懼<br />\n因為中共恐懼香港人爭取民主及公義既決心<br />\n佢咪出招恐嚇你地 叫你地唔好再講 唔敢再講<br />\n其實睇番呢家 中共呢一招都仲好有用<br />\n8964之後 97移民潮 到呢家國安法立法後<br />\n個個急急腳走 一家大細去移民<br />\n亦都為自己訂立左自設既紅線<br />\n呢樣唔可以做 呢樣唔講得<br />\n怕會違反國安法<br />\n你問我呢家有咩做?<br />\n係阿 好似咩都無野好做咁<br />\n但我唔會去驚 我唔會去為自設紅線 <br />\n去比自己懼怕共產黨囉<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">怯 你就輸一世</span></span>"},{"pid":"93306b56a40367c5d6bbff6c1f9f35d4d4e6774a","tid":2355594,"uid":146351,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"睇到好多人好驚好驚<br />\n個個準備移民 或去其他國家申請政治庇護<br />\n講真 有咩好驚?<br />\n你地記唔記得自己14年/19年為咩企出黎?<br />\n如果呢家就驚既話 咁點解果陣要企出黎? <br />\n老實講我係19年幾場光復遊行<br />\n同幾場和理非集會既申請人<br />\n更被捕過坐過?<br />\n有咩好驚?"},{"pid":"f0d120b2f86bda283bfa729e30f766aa782f261e","tid":2355594,"uid":147010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9yo6iS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9yo6iS.png&h=8d56dd60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4ccfa21abe16aac403c394599a1bff863818965","tid":2355594,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWrDEzg.gif&amp;h=e7205282&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"344b9a2169af4d7b6ea7dea8e8af814192f70b0d","tid":2355594,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ccfa21abe16aac403c394599a1bff863818965","tid":2355594,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A